    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment for the non-cannulated pedicle screw FEA model is Accepted. The model ensemble demonstrates sufficient fidelity for the intended regulatory submission purpose. Preliminary comparisons between FEA predictions and experimental data from N=11 constructs are favorable across all three QoIs. The shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is considered acceptable given the medium model influence and medium decision consequence classification. The assessment team is satisfied that the modeling framework is fit for purpose.",
